title: Band-tailed Pigeon Habitat, Utah Division of Wildlife Resources
name: Band-tailed Pigeon Habitat, Utah Division of Wildlife Resources
description: Habitat shapefile for band-tailed pigeon from the Utah Division of Wildlife Resources. Uploaded as shp, dbf, shx, and prj files.

properties.COMMENTS: Polygon drawn based on actual observations of band-tailed pigeons in certain areas and upon biologists' knowledge of suitable habitat. Note that not all vegetation types within this broad polygon are suitable for pigeons.
